Sophiya Haque https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sophiya_Haque 0 Sophiya Haque (14 June 1971 – 17 January 2013) was an English actress, singer, video jockey and dancer. She is best known for playing the role of Poppy Morales in Coronation Street between 2008 and 2009.
